  "title": "docs(rangeSlider): update story",
  "body": "This updates the [`rangeSlider`](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/range-slider/js/) stories to make them more representative of what the widget offers:\r\n\r\n- remove non-existant `templates.header` option\r\n- remove custom `tooltips` option by default\r\n- update the `step` value to be more usable and remove `pips` for the story so that it's less confusing (the step is not aligned with the pip)",
